CHAT.comment: Freeplay. Mother and Child are playing on the living+room floor with a box of experimenter provided toys. First they play with a small truck with plastic shapes that fit through the sides and the top. Then they play with Cookie Monster and Ernie puppets. The child's speech is fairly comprehensible.

u.a: tries to fit shape in side .
tries to put piece in , hands piece to Mother .
tries to put it in wrong hole .
tries to put it in herself , cries .
opens truck and pours out shapes , then closes truck .
tries to put shapes in back .
As Mother takes new toy from box .
tries to take other puppet out of bag .
takes other puppet out of bag .
high pitched while holding up puppet .
Both use high-pitched voices with puppets .
